SMS,Gateway,is,an,SMS,messaging,provider,Developers,can,use,the,service,to,integrate,SMS,messaging,into,their,applications,Because,the,service,is,based,in,North,America,they,claim,that,messages,will,not,be,blocked,or,filtered,The,service,can,be,used,to,send,appointment,reminders,provide,notifications,during,critical,equipment,outages,keep,staff,informed,when,traveling,and,tell,customers,about,upcoming,offers,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON